##### Company

Skymosity is a weather marketing platform providing web-based technology including email triggers, site personalization, sms triggers, and analytics for marketers to target based on weather.

##### Integration

The solution built specifically for Optimizely enables users to easily personalize their site and conduct A/B tests based on weather, all from within Optimizely.

